Copyright (C) 2013 Shay Zakov, Marcus Kinsella, and Vineet Bafna, itself
licensed under GPL-3.0.

- src/decision.cpp: the core algorithm (decisionFold/hasPalindromeConcatenation)
  is a line-by-line port of BFBCalculator.decisionBFB/decisionFold and
  Signature.hasPalindromeConcatenation from that project.
- src/distance.cpp: the weighted/noisy search is an original design (a
  Pareto-frontier branching search built on top of the ported decisionFold
  core above), rather than a port of BFBFinder's own noisy-search code
  (Signature.heaviestBFBVector); the Poisson error-model weight function is
  ported from PoissonErrorModel.weight(). As a combined/derivative work
  incorporating GPL-3.0 code, this file is likewise distributed under
  GPL-3.0.
